    %% External flows
    User -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token / Client Cert"| APIServer

    %% Control plane to controller
    APIServer -->|"HTTPS/9443<br/>TLS (self-managed)<br/>API server client cert<br/>AdmissionReview"| WebhookPort

    %% Controller to API server
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token<br/>CRUD: JobSets, CRDs, NetPol"| APIServer

    %% Controller to training pods
    Controller -->|"HTTP/28080<br/>plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy-restricted<br/>Progression tracking"| TrainingPods

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (insecureSkipVerify)<br/>No auth<br/>PodMonitor"| Metrics

